The Hub [[Missions|Plot]] explores a new gate network technology.

Completing the Hub requires significant resources and at the end you should have a well tuned trade network.

In the course of the plot you are granted access to [[Unknown Sector (The Hub)]].

==Starting Conditions==
*Arrive in just about any Boron sector with the following ranks:
*Boron rank 8 ([[Reputation#Boron|King's Knight]])
*Trade rank 6 ([[Ranks|Apprentice Trader]])
TIP: If you have problems with the Plot not starting, go to the Boron sectors in the south east.

